{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"syntax":"C"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference"},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusproxysignalname\/notify"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO19DBusProxySignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Case","title":"DBusProxySignalName.notify"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxySignalName\/notify"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxySignalName"]]},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusProxySignalName":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusproxysignalname","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"DBusProxySignalName